title: How To Make Za'atar | Dalia Dogmoch
description:
Syrian German Dalia Dogmoch makes everyday recipes with a Middle Eastern twist.  Here she shows you how to make Zaatar - a spice used in many of her dishes.
If you’d like to see more of Dalia on the channel let us know in the comments box below

Ingredients:
¼ cup dried sumac
¼ cup dried thyme
2 tbsp dried oregano
1 tbsp dired marjoram
2 tbsp toasted sesame seeds
¼ tbsp coarse sea salt
2-3 tbsp olive oil
